Class Summary
City The City class used in this project.
CityMapper The wrapped Mapper of cities, which includes both two BSTs for fast city name/coordinate query, and a PR-Quadtree that supports a set of spatial operation.
PRQuadTree A PR Quadtree that maps City objects into a given region; it also provides a couple of operations concerning the tree structure.
